{"tid":1496450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[集思廣益]有冇一首屬於香港嘅歌？","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T20:32:40.000Z","uid":27036,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4945760a74bd6d1a4e922621c6339bc021309d","tid":1496450,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"人地通常有自己嘅國歌，有事發生時全部一齊唱可以團結大家，亦係一種身份嘅認同。<br />\n<br />\n作為香港人，我地欠缺咗一首代表到我地嘅歌。<br />\n<br />\n我地香港有咁多音樂人才，唔知係呢一刻會唔會有人可以為香港寫一首屬於香港嘅自由之歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講明先唔係要今天我果d唱到無哂鬥志嘅歌，要一首聽完會愛上做香港人嘅歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952bfdd70606a5156b4a9a559b2f45642ea125b5","tid":1496450,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4945760a74bd6d1a4e922621c6339bc021309d","tid":1496450,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"人地通常有自己嘅國歌，有事發生時全部一齊唱可以團結大家，亦係一種身份嘅認同。<br />\n<br />\n作為香港人，我地欠缺咗一首代表到我地嘅歌。<br />\n<br />\n我地香港有咁多音樂人才，唔知係呢一刻會唔會有人可以為香港寫一首屬於香港嘅自由之歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講明先唔係要今天我果d唱到無哂鬥志嘅歌，要一首聽完會愛上做香港人嘅歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7387d6cb509319708c18f6ea7b3177f8829e73","tid":1496450,"uid":28451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"地踎搖滾"},{"pid":"5d0c267664126f3198517f72e24dad85cba0999d","tid":1496450,"uid":206386,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"海闊天空<br />\n<br />\n我知比人膠化左廿年<br />\n但最多人識<br />\n歌詞又夠有意思"},{"pid":"73aa965e10aef74569803e3ad10d4bc1f534adbb","tid":1496450,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dis